rancho mirage calif is among the conference hosts 
this is the second meeting for the experts who first exchanged 
information at an april conference in moscow attended by about 100 
americans 
the conference was the brainchild of father luis dolan a roman 
catholic priest who coordinates soviet exchanges for the wainwright 
house in rye ny dolan who has visited the soviet union several 
times said some of the questions he heard most often on his early 
trips had to do with alcoholism 
something just touched me here he said striking his chest 
with a fist when they said can we organize a conference 
the soviet delegates include scientists recovering alcoholics 
