7547 cents a pound feeder cattle were 15 cent to 45 cent lower 
with november at 8355 cents a pound hogs were 15 cent to 65 
cent lower with december at 5067 cents a pound frozen pork 
bellies were 175 cents to 2 cents lower with february at 6255 
cents a pound 
